channel.description: The home of "The Scenesters" and all sorts of indie music fun! We've got Punk, Hardcore, Metal, Emo, Indie, and Rockabilly. Lots of shows to satisfy the pickiest of music ManicLab.com is the home of the Scenesters, "Set the World Ablaze" MP3 comp and eZine, "Scene Points" photo rating, "Band Name Generator".
